          <li>Two Japanese bands confirmed: Lovebites and Broken By The Scream. Validates Two Engine Model thesis. Both are content priorities.</li>
          <li>Both continue straight to London the days after the festival: Broken By The Scream at The Dome (Tufnell Park) on Sunday August 2, Lovebites at O2 Academy Islington on Monday August 3. Wacken and London back-to-back for both bands. Broken By The Scream M&amp;G confirmed at The Dome.</li>
          <li>Broken By The Scream signed to Metal Blade Records in 2026. Major label inflection point, reinforces the Two Engine Model thesis.</li>
          <li>Arch Enemy playing with Lauren Hart replacing Alissa White-Gluz. Connects to Leadership episode thesis where Alissa left two days after that episode launched.</li>
