          <li>Sabaton announced Grand Swedish Arena Tour 2027 on June 12, tickets went on sale June 15. Wacken closing-headliner slot August 1 unchanged.</li>
          <li>Gannondorf, the US Metal Battle 2026 champion, is a San Diego avant-garde black metal band. They won June 13 at Brick By Brick taking both judges and crowd. Kevin attended. They open the international Metal Battle tournament on the Headbangers Stage Wednesday July 29 at 11:25.</li>
